FBIS4-42867 "drweu111_p_94005" FBIS-WEU-94-111 Daily Report 8 Jun 1994 GREECE Meets With Arsenis Meets With Arsenis NC0806172294 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 1500 GMT 8 Jun 94 NC0806172294 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Greek BFN [Text] Finnish Defense Minister Elizabeth Rehn, who is on a three-day official visit to our country, had talks with the political leadership of the Ministry of National Defense today. Mrs. Rehn, who is the only female defense minister in the world, met with Greek National Defense Minister Yerasimos Arsenis and discussed defense-related issues.
